data.description: **SALE FAILED SO HERE IS YOUR 2ND CHANCE AT THIS PROPERTY!  MOVE IN READY! BIGGEST TOWNHOME YARD YOU'VE EVERY SEEN! IMMACULATE AND SPOTLESS FROM THE WALLS TO THE CARPETS!!** This beautiful townhome is nestled in the middle of a coveted subdivision in Eagle Mountain! This sweet end unit is close to everything, schools, grocery and convenience stores, doctors, dentists, you name it! The community has its own private park, and is next to another beautiful park just steps away! The vaulted ceiling living room is big, open, full of light, and It gives you the feeling of being home the minute you walk through the front door! There is a pass-through window to the kitchen from the living room so you always feel a part of what's going on in this cute kitchen. There are lots of cabinets in here, a new dishwasher, and plenty of room to move around in here and create goodies with your favorite baker! The dining room has ample room to have guests over, and flows nicely into the biggest back yard in the community! There are gorgeous garden boxes back here, and in the front yard as well, that the current owners actually designed, and made themselves out of a giant log! Downstairs is another family room/bedroom so you can have guests stay over in their own wonderful space, including their own beautiful, full bathroom! On the second level, we find three bedrooms, and a bathroom. A spacious hallway connects each of them and each room is oversized, especially the primary bedroom. This room sits alone in its own corner of the house, and has beautiful windows to welcome the morning! The primary bedroom also has its own ensuite that is super cute. The set up of this house is so efficient, and convenient, and the neighborhood is fabulous. People don't move from here very often for good reason. Don't miss out on this well kept, updated, special townhome in a great location!
